Deborah Ryan https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Deborah_Ryan 0 Not to be confused with Debby Ryan
Deborah Ryan, more widely known as "Not that Deborah Ryan", is an American actress who appeared in a number of television shows and movies during the late 1970s through the early 1980s. She had a starring role in the 1978 TV movie Kiss Meets the Phantom of the Park.
